<c74object name='sp.shaker~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Physical model of a maraca/shaker</digest>
    <description>Physical model of a maraca/shaker.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.shaker~</o> object is a physical model of a maraca. It can also be used to create hi-hat or snare sounds depending on the settings. The model is activated by a generated impulse, live input, or a combination of both, which serves to further shape the resultant sound..</p>
</discussion>

